items.title: House to hold votes on funding package to end partial government shutdown
items.description: The House will hold votes on Tuesday to try to reopen the government after it partially shut down over the weekend.

items.title: Disney names Josh D'Amaro CEO, Dana Walden president and chief creative officer
items.description: The company's next CEO will succeed current chief executive Bob Iger.

items.title: WATCH:  Behind the scenes before Westminster's best in show
items.description: ABC News' Danny New tours the 150th Westminster Kennel Club Dog Show, meeting people from around the U.S. and exotic dog breeds that are new to him.

items.title: WATCH:  Houses washed away in North Carolina's Outer Banks
items.description: Waterfront houses collapsed into the ocean as a powerful winter storm lashed North Carolina's Outer Banks.

items.title: WATCH:  Floridians picking up cold-stunned iguanas amid wintry weather
items.description: Authorities have given people a special dispensation to bring specimens of the invasive species to collection points.
